# Input

```jsx
(
	<div
		bar='foo'
		baz={"foo"}
	>
		"123"
	</div>
)

```


# Options

```json
{
  "$schema": "../../../../../../../packages/@biomejs/biome/configuration_schema.json",
  "javascript": {
    "formatter": {
      "quoteStyle": "single",
      "jsxQuoteStyle": "single"
    }
  }
}
```

# Formatted

```jsx
<div bar='foo' baz={'foo'}>
	"123"
</div>;

```
